The Fall 2017 White House Internship Program application is now open. The application portal will remain open until June 16, 2017. The internship program will run from September 6 to December 8, 2017. Applicants must be at least 18 years old, U.S. citizens, and meet certain criteria to apply. The selection process is competitive, based on commitment to public service, leadership, and commitment to the Trump Administration. For more information and frequently asked questions, visit the White House website.